  "encoding": "windows-1252",
  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> <strong>The Waste\n        Land</strong></font><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p><font>According to Eliot, the title was\n        suggested by Miss Jessie L. Weston's <em>From Ritual to\n        Romance</em>, a work of literary criticism exploring the\n        pagan and Christian roots of the Grail legend. See also\n        Eliot's own note, below.</font></p>\n<p><font><em>reference topics</em></font></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><font>full publication history</font></td>\n<td><a href=\"publication_data.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><font>discussion of the title</font></td>\n<td><a href=\"title_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"ENl1.htm\">Eliot's\n                Note to the title</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"title_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Waste_A.htm\"><font>back to \"The Waste Land\" </font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
  "text": "The Waste Land According to Eliot, the title was suggested by Miss Jessie L. Weston's From Ritual to Romance , a work of literary criticism exploring the pagan and Christian roots of the Grail legend. See also Eliot's own note, below. reference topics full publication history discussion of the title Eliot's Note to the title back to \"The Waste Land\"",
